org.apache.fineract.commands.annotation

Annotation Type CommandType


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Documented
public @interface CommandType
    Specifies the command type for the annotated class.

    The entity name (e.g. CLIENT, SAVINGSACCOUNT, LOANPRODUCT) and the action (e.g. CREATE, DELETE) must be given.
    Since:
    15.06
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Markus Geiss
